where ere thou have be , here or in yon world manifest , can thou tell what be , or what be or what be to come ? no thing shall last and there be thing that shall never change . history be write in blood , yet be battle really lose on the battlefield ? can thou tell me whence thou come and where thou go and what be , or what be , or what be to come ? for everything remain as it never be . ________________ name Otherworld Artist Eluveitie album everything Remain [ as it never be ]